cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.IR 

This paper is about natural language processing tasks, specifically joint Chinese word segmentation and part-of-speech tagging. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a neural network model, which suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the use of convolutional and pooling layers indicates that it could be related to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed model on different datasets, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
